**Cursed Civilian** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
If the Cursed Civilian is attacked by a lycan, they will turn into a wolf instead of dying.
__Details__
The Cursed Civilian is part of the townsfolk team, however they may betray their team at any moment.
If attacked any other way than by a lycan, the Cursed Civilian will die as usual.
